replies.body:
That symbol signifies that player is the current **owner** of the club. The other ones that **aren't** gold means that they're an **officer** in the club.

Check out our [Clubs Guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/207994746-Guide-to-Clubs) for more information on this system. Let me know if you have any questions.
It means the person who created the club
